invalid type: string "Question: What purpose do \"Optional Fields\" serve in the PINT AE framework?\r\n\r\nAnswer: Optional fields are not strictly required for tax compliance but provide additional business context and transparency for records and auditing. Examples include the Actual Delivery Date (IBT-072), Item Attributes (IBG-32), and Country of Origin for goods (IBT-159).\r\n\r\nw_progresss
